TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Update Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE WIP SET FINISHING_PLANT = :TU.FINISHING_PLANT, CUT_START_DATE = :TU.CUT_START_DATE, CUT_DUE_DATE = :TU.CUT_DUE_DATE, SEW_START_DATE = :TU.SEW_START_DATE, SEW_DUE_DATE = :TU.SEW_DUE_DATE WHERE PROD_ORDER_NO=:TU.PROD_ORDER_NO AND RECORD_TYPE='HEADER'
